## ğŸ¯ Aim
To build a responsive image gallery using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that supports lightbox viewing, next/previous navigation, hover effects, and category filtering.

---

## ğŸ“– Description
This project creates a modern image gallery displayed in a responsive grid layout.  
Users can click on any image to open it in a lightbox popup. Navigation buttons allow moving to the next or previous image.  
Hover effects and smooth transitions improve the visual experience. Category filter buttons help sort images.

